headline: Trump Wants RFK Jr. To 'Go Wild' On Health Care. What This Means For Biotech Stocks.
summary: Robert F. Kennedy Jr. is the new Health Secretary. From fluoride, vaccines and beef tallow, here's how he might "go wild" on biotech stocks.

headline: Biogen (BIIB) Soars 5.7%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: Biogen (BIIB) was a big mover last session on higher-than-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions might not help the stock continue moving higher in the near term.
